---
// src/components/Features.astro
---
<section id="nosotros" class="bg-[#F9FAFB] py-16 lg:py-24 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-7xl">
    
    <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-titulo font-bold text-center text-[#183153] mb-16 lg:mb-24 ">
      ¿Qué puedes esperar de nosotros?
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-center relative">

      <div class="order-1 w-full grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-1 gap-8 lg:gap-24">
        
        <div class="group flex items-center justify-center lg:justify-end relative">
          <div class="text-center lg:text-right max-w-xs lg:pr-4 relative z-10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-titulo font-bold text-[#183153] mb-2">Agilidad</h3>
            
            <p class="font-body text-gray-600 text-base lg:text-lg leading-relaxed">
              Somos una compañía atenta e informada, reaccionamos rápido para adaptarnos.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="hidden md:block lg:hidden absolute top-full right-[15%] w-[40%] h-32 pointer-events-none z-0">
             <div class="w-full h-full border-l border-b border-[#8b9e8d]"></div>
             <div class="absolute bottom-0 -right-[4px] w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#8b9e8d]"></div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="hidden lg:flex items-center absolute -right-16 top-3 translate-x-2">
             <div class="w-16 h-[1px] bg-[#8b9e8d]"></div>
             <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#8b9e8d]"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group flex items-center justify-center lg:justify-end relative">
          <div class="text-center lg:text-right max-w-xs lg:pr-4 relative z-10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-titulo font-bold text-[#183153] mb-2">Vanguardia</h3>
            
            <p class="font-body text-gray-600 text-base lg:text-lg leading-relaxed">
              Somos modernos y tratamos de ir siempre un paso adelante en tendencias.
            </p>
          </div>

           <div class="hidden md:block lg:hidden absolute top-full left-[15%] w-[40%] h-32 pointer-events-none z-0">
             <div class="w-full h-full border-r border-b border-[#8b9e8d]"></div>
             <div class="absolute bottom-0 -left-[4px] w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#8b9e8d]"></div>
           </div>

           <div class="hidden lg:flex items-center absolute -right-16 top-3 translate-x-2">
             <div class="w-16 h-[1px] bg-[#8b9e8d]"></div>
             <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#8b9e8d]"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="order-2 flex justify-center relative z-20 py-4 lg:py-0">
        <div class="relative w-64 h-80 lg:w-80 lg:h-[500px] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border-4 border-white bg-white">
            <video
              src="/videos/tela_en_manos.mp4"
              poster="/images/TelaNosotros.png"
              playsinline
              autoplay
              muted
              loop
              preload="metadata"
              class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700 ease-out"
              aria-label="Rollos de tela en movimiento">
              Tu navegador no soporta la etiqueta de video.
            </video>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#8b9e8d]/10"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="order-3 w-full grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-1 gap-8 lg:gap-24">
        
        <div class="group flex items-center justify-center lg:justify-start relative">
           
           <div class="hidden md:block lg:hidden absolute bottom-full right-[15%] w-[40%] h-32 pointer-events-none z-0">
              <div class="w-full h-full border-l border-t border-[#8b9e8d]"></div>
              <div class="absolute top-0 -right-[4px] w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#8b9e8d]"></div>
           </div>

           <div class="hidden lg:flex items-center absolute -left-16 top-3 -translate-x-2">
             <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#8b9e8d]"></div> 
             <div class="w-16 h-[1px] bg-[#8b9e8d]"></div> 
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center lg:text-left max-w-xs lg:pl-4 relative z-10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-titulo font-bold text-[#183153] mb-2">Rapidez</h3>
            
            <p class="font-body text-gray-600 text-base lg:text-lg leading-relaxed">
              Realiza tu pedido y recíbelo con la eficiencia logística que necesitas.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group flex items-center justify-center lg:justify-start relative">
           
           <div class="hidden md:block lg:hidden absolute bottom-full left-[15%] w-[40%] h-32 pointer-events-none z-0">
              <div class="w-full h-full border-r border-t border-[#8b9e8d]"></div>
              <div class="absolute top-0 -left-[4px] w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#8b9e8d]"></div>
           </div>

           <div class="hidden lg:flex items-center absolute -left-16 top-3 -translate-x-2">
             <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#8b9e8d]"></div>
             <div class="w-16 h-[1px] bg-[#8b9e8d]"></div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center lg:text-left max-w-xs lg:pl-4 relative z-10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-titulo font-bold text-[#183153] mb-2">Arquitectura Sólida</h3>
            
            <p class="font-body text-gray-600 text-base lg:text-lg leading-relaxed">
              Tienes a todo el equipo de T3 detrás tuyo para asegurar el éxito.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>